{
  "stem": "25591.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot tell you of the non-Jews that I had in school as classmates, where they were on the spectrum in terms of bystanders who turned away or bystanders who felt for us but didn't do anything or felt they couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think that any of my Christian friends were active perpetrators of any of the horrors that preoccupied Hungary during that period.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These were silent spectators, or maybe in a modest way trying to help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I suspect once or twice in a-- in a very perfunctory way, but you see, the-- the horror was so overwhelming.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These boys like me were kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were 16, 17-year-old kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They must have been horrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe most of them had to be horrified, but they clearly had no power.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think if any of their parents had any power.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It-- it really didn't become a subject of discussion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I think-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think it would have been [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] very difficult to discuss it, both for them and-- and-- and for us because we could not blame them, but we clearly could not exonerate them or their parents or their grandparents, and-- and while we clearly remembered a great deal.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This particular school was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a school with a heavy Jewish enrollment, lots of Christian-Jewish friendships and relationships.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I personally feel that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] on the-- on-- on the spectrum, these were probably bystanders, mostly, if not all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] it's-- it's a very difficult thing to-- to answer because on the one hand, in a political sense, there are two Hungarian-Americans-- well, this is really not accurate because one of them was born here.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
